claim: Tom Felton acted in From the Rough in 1988.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He had roles in the minor films From the Rough  (  2011  )  and The Apparition  (  2012  )  , starred as James Ashford in the critically acclaimed period drama film Belle  (  2013  )  , followed by roles in In Secret  (  2014  )  and Against the Sun  (  2014  )  .
